http://www.lead-inst.org:80/sbsc/sept96/cwcpr.html 204.71.237.80 19970210111822 text/html 4444
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 11:19:06 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 27-Sep-96 19:06:52 GMT
