<li>The Heritage Foundation--House Spending Bill Falls Far Short of Promised Government Overhaul, Analysts Say. <a href="/heritage/news/approp.html">September 15, 1995</a>
<li>The Heritage Foundation--U.S.-Asian Commerce on the Rise Despite Trade War Fears.  <a href="/heritage/news/handbook.html">September 8, 1995</a>
<li>The Heritage Foundation--Benefits "Cap" Decreases Out-of-Wedlock Births, Analyst Says. <a href="/heritage/news/rect.html">September 7, 1995</a>
<li>The Heritage Foundation--House Farm Bill a "Good First Step" But More Needed, Analyst Says. <a href="/heritage/news/agbill.html">September 6, 1995</a> 
