http://www.lead-inst.org:80/wash_times/pruden.5_5.html 204.71.237.80 19970217125321 text/html 5518
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 17-Feb-97 12:54:17 GMT
Last-modified: Sunday, 28-Apr-96 17:35:22 GMT
