<DOCHDR>
http://www.lead-inst.org:80/wash_times/fields.8-4.html 204.71.237.80 19970217123932 text/html 5277
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 17-Feb-97 12:40:28 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 29-Jul-96 01:28:29 GMT
Content-length: 5094
