<DOCHDR>
http://www.lead-inst.org:80/discovery/regionaloly.html 204.71.237.80 19970217122522 text/html 7749
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 17-Feb-97 12:26:17 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 17-Feb-97 08:32:29 GMT
